    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, but it's a bit brief for a competitive debate level. my students need more depth to handle high-level rebuttals. can you expand on the economic side of this? specifically, how would a proponent argue that strict enforcement actually protects the domestic labor market and prevents wage depression for low-skilled workers?",
